INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('4251','117','ECS004251','华硕GTX650TIB-DC20C-2GD5  超公版','+','39','0','','100','0.000','0.00','1245.00','0.00','0','0','1','GTX650TI-B','','<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">为了填补GTX660~GTX650Ti之间的市场空缺及更好地与HD7850进行对位，英伟达在最近祭出中端新核心GTX650Ti Boost，使其6系列产品线填充更加完整的同时，也为沉寂已久的中端市场带来新一轮的角力，让消费者有了更多的选择。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425184502.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">在英伟达推出GTX650Ti BOOST后不久，华硕一口气就拿出了GTX650TIB-DC2-2GD5和GTX650TIB-DC2OC-2GD5两款新品，可见华硕对市场反应之灵敏及强大的研发实力。前段时间评测室收到了华硕的GTX650TIB-DC2OC-2GD5，让我们进行简单评测看看它实力如何。</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>华硕GTX650TIB-DC2OC-2GD5概览：</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425331254.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425466434.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425578081.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425678656.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">华硕的这一款显卡还是延续了华硕简洁而不浮夸的设计风格，整体以黑色为基色，散热器上搭配上经典的红色&ldquo;三道杠&rdquo;，给人以稳重大气之感。作为一款非公版卡，该卡散热器面积完全超过了显卡PCB，总体的造型还是挺大的，很容易与公版卡区分开。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425780493.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">受益于先进的制程，6系列N卡的PCB普遍较短小，相比于GTX650系列其他&ldquo;短半截&rdquo;的显卡，华硕的这一款显卡的PCB还是要长一些的，背面的元器件也很密集，少有空焊，还有4颗显存植在背板。背部上方的两根镀镍铜管也很显眼，可见该卡的做工不俗。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425888374.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115426006475.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115426102126.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">华硕GTX650TIB-DC2OC-2GD5采用了常见的DisplayPort+HDMI+2*DVI的输出接口搭配，相比于华硕之前的GTX650省去了VGA接口而增加了DP接口，这样的设计更符合这款显卡的定位和更能满足用户的使用需求。6PIN外接电源接口方面，这款显卡采用了和其他显卡不一样的设计，接口与电源线的卡口调换至PCB这一面，方便用户进行插拔操作，看来华硕的做工还是挺仔细的。</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>本期评测显卡天梯指引位置如下：</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115434865537.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>PConline显卡天梯图说明：</strong>华硕GTX650TIB DC2OC使用超公版设计，频率更高，在性能上领先于公版GTX650TI BOOST 和HD7850，所以在天梯图中如上图的位置。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-transform: none; word-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(64,64,64); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; padding-left: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img title=\"点击图片查看下一页\" alt=\"点击图片查看下一页\" src=\"http://image.xinmin.cn/2013/04/23/20130423115425466434.jpg\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px\" /></p>','images/201308/thumb_img/4251_thumb_G_1375635620935.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4251_G_1375635619971.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4251_G_1375635619656.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1375429361','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1376016578','5','','0','0','0','');
