form: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 622px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; height: 23px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/699042318/T2MYNJXnNaXXXXXXXX_!!699042318.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 麦博<span>M-111</span>纪念版是一款<span>2.1</span>音箱，由<span>1</span>个低音单元和<span>2</span>个卫星单元以及线控器构成。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">麦博<span>M-111</span>纪念版音箱外观设计比较独特，给人一种既时尚、又稳重的感觉，黑色的主色调配上环形的橙红色点缀，看起来非常舒服，丝毫没有沉闷感。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">低音炮是<span>2.1</span>音箱最重要的部分，箱体为木质材质，音箱电路和<span>4</span>英寸的低音扬声器等都安置在里面。低音炮的外观秉承了传统的方正形状，但是前面板的棱角采用切面处理，低音扬声器网罩顶端设计成弧形，下端为音箱的倒相孔，政体感觉典雅而不古板。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">主箱正面上端为麦博的<span>LOGO</span>，下端为前置的倒相孔，倒相孔采用镜面漆技术处理，边缘还加入了醒目的橙红色圆环，在黑色背景下非常突出。主箱背面也比较简单，提供了音频输入接口、左右声道输出接口、开关和电源输入线，产品的铭牌和<span>3C</span>认证等标签也贴在这里。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">和主箱不同，卫星箱风格要活泼一些，抛弃了传统的长方体型设计，更想一只摆在桌面的相框，只不过放相片的部分换成了<span>2.5</span>英寸的扬声器单元而已。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">卫星箱正面采用了镜面技术处理，亮度和光洁度都非常好，几乎可以当镜子用。箱体其它部位较薄，而扬声器部分突出，很有层次感。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">M111</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(51,51,51); font-size: 12pt\">线控器淡绿色那条线用来连接电脑等音频输出接口，而另外黑色的那条则连接到低音炮音频输入接口，由此实现线控功能。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','images/201308/thumb_img/4336_thumb_G_1375861718682.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4336_G_1375861718728.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4336_G_1375861718483.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1375861718','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1375861764','68','','0','0','0','');
INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('4337','73','ECS004337','麦博M200','+','20','0','','100','0.000','0.00','140.00','0.00','0','0','1','麦博 电脑音箱 笔记本音箱 2.1声道 100-199','','<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;<img align=\"absMiddle\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/629441792/T2uxmdXm8aXXXXXXXX_!!629441792.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">麦博的M-200使用了与七年前麦博（当时的麦兰）同样一个型号的方法出场，最终想表达的是麦博对这款最新的M-200产品的信心。</font></p>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ProductImages/Big/0/91/000091059.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ProductImages/NonstandardMiddle/0/91/000091053.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ProductImages/NonstandardMiddle/0/91/000091054.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\">从外形来看，M-200的线条非常明快，低音炮方方正正，采用黑色木质箱体，惟一的点缀是箱体前表面的麦博的LOGO。低音炮的摆放方式有点特别，长方体的长边横向摆放，这样在桌面上会显得横向占地比较大，但外形的视觉效果就比较特别了。M-200的调节电位器放在音箱的右侧，使用上非常顺手。</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">\r\n<div align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ProductImages/NonstandardMiddle/0/91/000091051.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ProductImages/NonstandardMiddle/0/91/000091050.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /></font></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\">M-200卫星箱的设计在造型上非常简单，但它却巧妙的将箱体表面做成斜面，让扬声器具有了一定的仰角。这样，即使是一个没有支架的普通塑料箱也可以具有更好的指向人耳的物理外形。</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"4\">麦博M-200主客观测评</font></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><img border=\"1\" src=\"http://img2.pcpop.com/ArticleImages/400x300/0/150/000150641.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px; border-left: black 1px; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px; border-right: black 1px\" alt=\"\" /></font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">频响曲线：</strong>M-200在10K以上的高频段有一定幅度的拔高，而在其他中高频及中频的两个区域波动都不算大。低音炮方面，</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><font size=\"4\">100Hz附近的强度稍好于M-600。但整体声音风格，M-200却与M-600不太相同。</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"4\">主观听感</font></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"4\">麦博M200，一款被热炒的产品，经过测试我们发现M200的确也有一些被&ldquo;炒作&rdquo;的资本，概括来说，M200的声音可能要好过其他几款M系列的产品。M200声音风格与M600以及没有参加本次测试的M500都有很大的不同，M200的声音相对要放得开许多。相对而言，M200的中高频比较明亮，但是又稍显单薄，高频有人为的拔高，但在大多数情况下并不会刺耳。难得的是，M200的功率充足，在大音量下比其他同价位音箱有好得多的声音，低音的质量也可以有所保证。作为一款低端产品，它的声音表现令我们非常满意。</font></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"4\">综合评价</font></strong></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" align=\"center\"><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><font size=\"4\">我们可以先不去管七年前麦博M200有过怎样的辉煌，但从音质来看今天的M200拥有不错的水准。外观方面，M200并没有什么特别，但在细节方面就要比大多数低端产品处理的好，如箱体材料、电位器的质量等等。而我们前面提到的低端音箱密封不好，由于漏气而影响音质的情况没有出现在M200上。今天的M200能否延续七年前&ldquo;麦蓝&rdquo;M200的经典，我们并不好预测。但从产品的整体素质来说，麦博的M200在同类产品中占很大优势。</font></strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; backgroun