homa, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">新装机最佳选择</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">麦博新版</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">试用手记</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　【天极</span><span><span>Yesky</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">华南评测室】作为国内著名的多媒体厂商，一线大厂麦博每年都会推出几款</span><span>M</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">系列的针对装机主流市场的新品，虽然机型相同，外观和品质也对前版多有继承，但整体功能却是一代更比一代强。最近新上市的经典的</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">的</span><span>07</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">版不但外型较</span><span>06</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">版大有改进，音效更是有了显著的进步，可谓低端装机的首选机型之一。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span>prefix = v ns = &quot;urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml&quot; prefix = o ns = &quot;urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office&quot;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img02.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i2/712460296/T21GBMXdJcXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　我们在月初的时候就已经报道了</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">登陆广州的新闻，今天笔者收到了麦博寄来的评测产品，虽然属于低端产品，但麦博在整体配备上可是一点都不含糊，</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">的包装箱就做的相当精致漂亮，与其他同类产品简陋的包装形成鲜明的对比，其分量更是了得，</span><span>4.4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">公斤的重量让笔者搬起来累的气喘吁吁。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">技术参数一览：</span><span><br />\r\n*</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">功放参数：</span><span><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">输出功率</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>16W+12Wx2 RMS<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">频率响应</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>35Hz-20KHz<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">输入灵敏度</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>400mV<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">失真度</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>&lt;0.3% (1W 1KHz)<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">信噪比</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>&gt;80dB<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">隔离度</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>&gt;45dB<br />\r\n*</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">扬声器单元：</span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">低音</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>5&quot;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">防磁</span><span><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">高音</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>2&quot; x 2<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">防磁</span><span><br />\r\n*</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">音频输入</span><span>: 2 RCA</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">插孔</span><span><br />\r\n*</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">音频输出</span><span>: 2 RCA</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">插孔</span><span><br />\r\n*</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">产品尺寸</span><span>:<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">低音</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>270x160x215mm<br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">高音</span><span><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>76x70x160mm</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">的低音炮算是入门级产品里面份量很足的了，规规矩矩的大木箱使用了</span><span>9mm</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">厚的中密度纤维板制成，体积也很可观，达到了长宽高分别为</span><span>270</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">、</span><span>160</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">和</span><span>215mm</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/712460296/T2RqFMXjtbXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　</span><span>07</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">版</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">在外观上沿袭了麦博</span><span>M</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">系列的一贯风格，黑色的笔直线条显得十分硬朗沉稳，和麦博音箱准确而沉稳的风格取向很匹配。低音炮规正的长方体造型棱角分明，前面板上光亮的弧型贴板简洁明快，使得整体风格看来既稳重又不显生硬沉闷。下方是电源显示灯和音量控制旋钮。低音部分使用的是长冲程的</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">寸低音扬声器，加之厚重的箱体，想来音效一定值得称道。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/712460296/T2tqJMXclbXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　背板的设置同样简洁，除了电源开关和音频输入输出的两组莲花头外，还有一个低音增益旋纽，有一目了然的明快感。因为没有散热装置，铝质的背板就负责起了散热的功能，笔者曾担心使用时间长了背板会很热，但在后来的试听过程中发现散热效果因为低音炮的硕大而表现得比预想的要好些。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/712460296/T28qJMXntaXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　卫星箱的设计则时尚了许多，全塑封结构的箱体整个采用圆弧型，线条流畅。大小和手掌差不多，很宜于桌面的摆放。而微微上扬的箱体能使声音具有更好的指向性，轻易就能营造出良好的听音环境。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/712460296/T2FWNMXklaXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">　　</span><span>M300</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">采用的是一款</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">寸的全防磁喇叭，使用了玻纤复合纸盆，折环较软，这个单元的声音特性是温暖柔和，声音表现细腻的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\"><img align=\"middle\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/712460296/T21aRMXdBaXXXXXXXX_!!712460296.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>','images/201308/thumb_img/4342_thumb_G_1375925209350.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4342_G_1375925209178.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4342_G_1375925208881.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1375925208'