rgin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings; color: #ffcc99\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #ffcc99\">支持24DB双天线无线WIFI</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings; color: #ffcc99\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #ffcc99\">支持触摸按键功能</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings; color: #000000\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: #000000\">支持USB键盘和USB鼠标操作</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">BD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">蓝光原盘播放，支持BDMV全功能</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">导航菜单</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">BD简易导航菜单：支持多字幕、多音轨切换，&nbsp;以及章节选择功能</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: -21pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 21pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family: wingdings\">&Oslash;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">支持7.1次世代高清音轨源码输出，支持</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">Dolby&nbsp;True&nbsp;HD</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">DTS-HD&nbsp;MA</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">LPCM</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">Dolby&nbsp;Digital&nbsp;Pl