der-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.datastorage.com.cn/UploadFiles/img/X250/X250-packing.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"503\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.datastorage.com.cn/UploadFiles/img/mode/10%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"24\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">* X250传输接口：USB 3.0</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">1.其向下兼容USB 2.0，即可以连接到USB 2.0接口的计算机上进行使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">2. USB 3.0数据线进行连接时，请确认接口连接到位。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">3.可以使用USB 2.0数据线进行连接使用，且为USB 2.0的速度。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">*当使用USB 2.0接口连接使用时，由于USB 2.0接口供电只有500mA，低于USB 3.0接口的900mA，则有可能出现供电不足，此时可以配上一个5V/1A~2A，外径：3.25mm，内径：1.3mm，内正外负的电源进行使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">*当计算机无USB 3.0接口时，可以通过在PC电脑主板上安装一个PCI-E USB 3.0转接卡，并对转接卡进行正确的驱动后方可使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">* X250硬盘格式化：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">1. Windows系统：请右键点击我的电脑-管理-磁盘管理，找到相应的硬盘，即可对硬盘进行初始化、格式化。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); list-style-type: none; text-indent: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/26px \'tahoma geneva arial helvetica\'; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(85,85,85); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\">2. MAC系统：请在应用程序-实用程序-磁盘工具，找到相应的硬盘，并选择抹掉，即可格式化硬盘</span></p>','images/201308/thumb_img/4460_thumb_G_1376373852996.jpg','images/201308/goods_img/4460_G_1376373852681.jpg','images/201308/source_img/4460_G_1376373852873.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1376373852','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1376373852','0','','0','0','0','');
