; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">- 5.1 声道高保真音频 (Realtek ALC662 音频编码解码器)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#f5f5f5\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\"><b>局域网</b></td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">- PCIE x1 千兆网卡 10/100/1000 Mb/s<br />\r\n            - Realtek RTL8111E<br />\r\n            - 支持网线侦测<br />\r\n            - 支持 Energy Efficient Ethernet 802.3az<br />\r\n            - 支持 PXE</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr bgcolor=\"#dddddd\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\"><b>&nbsp;扩充 / 接口</b></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#f5f5f5\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\"><b>扩充插槽</b></td>\r\n            <td style=\"border-bottom-color: black; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-color: black; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-right-color: black; border-left-color: black; padding-top: 0px\">- 1 x PCI Express 2.0 x16 插槽 (PCIE1 x16 模式)<br />\r\n            - 1 x PCI 插槽<br />\r\n            - 支持 AMD Dual Graphics</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td bgcolor=\"#f5f5f5\" align=\"center\" style=\"border-bottom-colo