hite-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255,255,0)\">中关村评测报道：</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 26px/34px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测</h1>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">10nm级闪存+高频主控 三星EV0登场</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; font: 0px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><em style=\"font-style: italic\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;前不久三星发布新一代NGFF接口&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">SSD</a>，其读写速度高达1.<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">4GB</a>/秒，性能惊艳全场。我们从SSD和<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">主板</a>厂商的观望态度分析，英特尔推出的NGFF接口要么是恶魔，要么是天使。三星为此做了另一手准备，在现有SATA3.0接口上继续改良SSD，推出原有840系列SSD的升级版－－<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">三星840</a>&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD。</em></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/311/ceTI5gZAU992.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">巅峰性能爆发&nbsp;三星840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">1TB</a>&nbsp;SSD首测</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;升级改良版的三星840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD的最大容量翻倍至1TB，保留最小120GB容量；它在硬件层面上实现主控、闪存的换代，从根本上推动扩容、提高性能；最后它在独门的加速软件上着手，实现SSD闪存作为高速缓存，为深度应用环境提速做准备。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/116/292/ced75OjNnUxM.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD的硬件、性能改进明细</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这款改良性能的三星840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD包括120GB、<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">250GB</a>、<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a>、<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">750GB</a>和1TB共5种容量的<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>，本文测试的SSD即为该款1TB版本。下面我们将进入三星840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;1TB&nbsp;SSD的技术解析、性能对比分析以及点评总结环节。</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.125; font-family: 宋体; float: right; font-size: 12px\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">SSD 840 EVO（1TB）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">三星</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\" name=\"p3879534\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" /></a></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">诠释EVO 源自四位一体设计方案</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">三星840</a>&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">SSD</a>中的&ldquo;EVO&rdquo;全称是:Evolution，其含义是发展、进化的意思，恰如其分的反映它是由840系SSD的进化升级而来。另外&ldquo;EVO&rdquo;是一款跑车的品牌，也是速度的一种体现。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/722/cePmcYyTXU0r6.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&ldquo;主控、闪存、缓存、固件&rdquo;自主方案</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;那么三星如何实现进化升级？我们需要从三星的&ldquo;主控、闪存、缓存、固件&rdquo;四位一体的自主研发、生产谈起。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;●三核心ARM&nbsp;Cortex-R4主控</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/691/cePm7Z6ZRkv6E.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">三星S4</a>LN045X01-8030（MEX）主控芯片</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三星本身具备<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">手机</a>、平板ARM架构<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">处理器</a>的研发生产能力，MEX主控是在成熟的MDX方案基础上进一步提升频率。它内建三个ARM&nbsp;Cortex-R4核心，工作频率提升至400MHz。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;●世界最小10nm级&nbsp;高速闪存芯片</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/819/ceK2lmkFkkx6.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n三星3bit&nbsp;MLC高速闪存（每die为128Gbit）</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三星840&nbsp;EVO SSD采用世界最小10nm级&nbsp;高速闪存芯片，每die晶圆芯片为128Gbit(折合为16GB），每颗黑色的成品闪存采用MCP多芯片封装。<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">1TB</a>版本的单颗成品闪存含有8个die晶圆芯片，总容量达到128GB。<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 它基于Toggle&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">DDR2</a>.0闪存架构。与现有三星840系SSD相比，新款EVO&nbsp;SSD在连续写入性能方面提升了3倍之多。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;●最高支持<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">1GB</a>独立缓存</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2d.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/695/ce79IGKyPQpB2.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星1GB&nbsp;独立缓存</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SSD的独立缓存用于存放映射表，越大容量的SSD就需要将映射表编得越大，对缓存的容量有更大的需求。最大容量为512GB的三星840系列SSD，拥有512MB独立缓存。而到了最大容量为1TB的840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD，则拥有1GB独立缓存。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">●针对840和EVO的不同固件支持</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>MDX和MEX硬件参数上的不同，意味着840&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;SSD需要升级的原有固件（Upgraded&nbsp;firmware）。同时它为了匹配10nm级闪存，设计最新的、更先进的信号处理算法（latest&nbsp;generation&nbsp;Advanced&nbsp;Signal&nbsp;Processing）。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;进化结果：</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三星840&nbsp;EV0&nbsp;SSD通过四位一体的全面进化，迸发出强悍性能，仅写入速度一项就提高1.6-3.1倍之多，随机读写能力也有不同程度提高。下面我们进入相关测试成绩对比分析：</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.125; font-family: 宋体; float: right; font-size: 12px\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">SSD 840 EVO（1TB）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">三星</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\" name=\"p3879535\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" /></a></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">读写速度对比：双双突破500MB/s</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● ATTO Disk Benchmark最大读取测试</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">ATTO Disk Benchmark是一款优秀且免费的磁盘基准测试软件，支持对稳定性/突发性传输速率进行读写测试，适用于常规<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">硬盘</a>、RAID、USB闪存盘、移动存储卡等<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">产品</a>的读写性能测试。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"482\" height=\"576\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/116/877/cehvND5xR8gCs.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">三星840</a>&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">1TB</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">SSD</a>的</strong><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">ATTO 队列深度4测试</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"691\" style=\"border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2e.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/870/ceB1FMtQl8XGU.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">ATTO Benchmark读写对比</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">在ATTO Benchmark测试针对压缩算法，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星840PRO 512GB SSD与三星840 EVO 1TB SSD的最大读写速度不相上下，位列榜首、榜眼</strong>；美光M500 480GB SSD、三星840系<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a>&nbsp;SSD输在最大写入速度，排名第三和第四名。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"border-bottom: 1px; border-left: 1px; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; height: 1px; color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px; border-right: 1px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image: initial\" />\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● CrystalDiskMark</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">CrystalDiskMark是一款简单易用的硬盘性能测试软件，但测试项目非常全面，涵盖连续读写、512K和4KB数据包随机读写性能，以及队列深度（Queue Depth）为32的情况下的4K随机性能。队列深度描述的是硬盘能够同时激活的最大IO值，队列深度越大，实际性能也会越高。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"406\" height=\"368\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/116/878/ceoISWshsfdAc.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星840 EVO 1TB SSD CrystalDiskMark测试</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"891\" style=\"border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/871/ceOYqP9yVncpw.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">CrystalDiskMark持续读写速度PK</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">CrystalDiskMark测试针对非压缩算法，<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星840 EVO 1TB SSD换位首获头名，三星840PRO 512GB SSD屈居第二；</strong>美光M500 480GB SSD、三星840系500GB SSD仍未摆脱ATT0的排名格局。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 点评：</strong>三星840 EVO SSD的读写速度可圈可点，与840PRO SSD媲美。我们从表中还能看出，其实三星840系列SSD已经遭受美光M500 SSD的打压，而美光M500 SSD的最大容量版本高达960GB。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三星840 EVO SSD和美光M500 SSD在容量和性能上进行激烈对抗。三星此次拿出雷霆手段，尖端技术尽遣，那么它在读写能力有什么样的表现？我们继续进行分析。</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.125; font-family: 宋体; float: right; font-size: 12px\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">SSD 840 EVO（1TB）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">三星</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\" name=\"p3879536\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" /></a></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">AS SSD：9万IOPS数据吞吐量对比</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 随机读写性能是<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>的关键指标，其单位为IOPS，即每秒进行读写（I/O接口）操作的次数。我们从表中看到固态<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">硬盘</a>的每秒进行读写操作的次数是以万为单位进行计算，而传统的机械硬盘不足300 IOPS值。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● AS&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">SSD</a>&nbsp;Benchmark</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">AS SSD Benchmark是一个专门为SSD测试而设计的标准检测程序，因为它提供了很大的可定制性。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 它的成绩显示可以分为两种，一种是MB/秒的形式，另一种是IOPS形式。本次测试主要使用这款软件的IOPS随机读写功能，测试4K-64Thrd多任务随机读写 IOPS值。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br style=\"line-height: 0; font-size: 0px\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"462\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; cursor: pointer; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/879/ceAMIVhfRsV.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">三星840</a>&nbsp;EVO&nbsp;<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">1TB</a>&nbsp;SSD 读写IOPS值</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"859\" style=\"border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2a.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/872/ceCgljZRQx8i6.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">AS SSD Benchmark IOPS值对比</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 在AS SSD 读写能力测试对比中，三星840 EVO 1TB SSD稍逊于三星840PRO 512GB SSD，屈居第二；美光M500 480GB SSD、三星840系<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">500GB</a>&nbsp;SSD位列第三、第四名。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr style=\"border-bottom: 1px; border-left: 1px; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; height: 1px; color: rgb(51,51,51); border-top: 1px; border-right: 1px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; border-image: initial\" />\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">● AS SSD 总分PK</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AS SSD并不仅仅局限于测试SSD的I/0接口吞吐量，它可以根据SSD的整体读写速度、I/0接口吞吐量、access time寻道时间，对SSD进行整体性能评估分数。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"462\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2c.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/880/ceRqf2LLusXvA.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">三星840 EVO 1TB SSD &ldquo;AS SSD&rdquo; 总分 1213分</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"782\" style=\"border-bottom: black 0px solid; border-left: black 0px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 0px solid; border-right: black 0px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2b.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/873/cerH2Hy0Xs8hg.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">AS SSD总分对比</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; AS SSD总分整合&ldquo;类似CrystalDiskMark的持续读写速度&rdquo;与&ldquo;AS SSD IOPS值&rdquo;，因此本项考核较为综合。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD凭借更为出色的持续读写速度，不输三星840PRO 512GB SSD的读写能力（IOPS），重获第一名。三星840PRO 512GB SSD位列第二；美光M500 480GB SSD、三星840系500GB SSD位列第三、第四名。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"巅峰性能爆发 三星840 EVO 1TB SSD首测\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://2f.zol-img.com.cn/product/116_500x2000/889/ce0GfEvQWhewY.jpg\" /></a><br />\r\n<b>一块三星840 EVO SSD 读写能力相当于200块机械硬盘</b></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;点评：</strong>三星840 EVO 1TB SSD的读写能力表现相当抢眼，可以和三星最强的840PRO 512GB SSD相提并论。其AS SSD总分进入顶尖SSD的1200分序列，并且微微超越三星840PRO 512GB SSD。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 美光M500 480GB SSD的读写能力与AS SSD总分小超三星840系500GB SSD。至此，三星840系SSD已在读写速度、读写能力这两大指标全面落后美光M500 SSD。中国市场急需三星840 EVO SSD驰援！</p>\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom: rgb(194,217,242) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 4px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); margin-top: 20px; text-indent: 0px; padding-left: 5px; font: 14px/25px 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.125; font-family: 宋体; float: right; font-size: 12px\">产品：<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">SSD 840 EVO（1TB）</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">三星</a>&nbsp;<a style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\">固态硬盘</a>&nbsp;<a target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(19,75,160); text-decoration: none\" name=\"p3879537\"><img alt=\"回到顶部阅读\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-image: initial\" src=\"http://icon.zol.com.cn/doc/2010/top.png\" /></a></span>\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">PCMark基准测试对比：首破9万分</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-indent: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">1、PCMark Vantage<a style=\"border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-decoration: none\">硬盘</a>模拟测试<br />\r\n亮点：首次突破9万分大关</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; ba